# 📚 Library Management System – Frontend (React.js)

This is the **frontend** of my full-stack **Library Management System** project, built using **React, Redux Toolkit, and Bootstrap**. The app is designed for both users and admins to manage book borrowing, reviews, and analytics in a clean and responsive UI.

---

##  Live App

 [👉 View Live App Here](https://frontend-library-management-system.vercel.app/)

 **Demo Admin Login:**
- Email: demo.admin@lms.com 
- Password: Demo@Lms2025

Or just click the **"Try as Demo Admin"** button on the login page!

---

##  Tech Stack (Frontend)

- **React.js**
- **Redux Toolkit**
- **React Router**
- **React Bootstrap**
- **Chart.js**
- **Axios**
- **Typewriter Effect**

---

##  Key Features

###  User Features:
- Register and login
- Browse and borrow books
- View borrowed books
- Submit and view reviews
- Add/Edit profile picture

### 🛠 Admin Features:
- Dashboard with charts and summaries
- Add/edit/delete books (protected)
- Manage user reviews
- View borrowing stats by week/category
- Promote/Demote/Delete Users

### 🧪 Demo Mode:
- Safe login with restricted permissions
- **Delete/edit/book actions disabled**
- Warning banner and disabled buttons for visual feedback

