## Folder Structure
├── components/ # Reusable UI components

├── features/ # Redux features (auth, user, books, reviews)

├── pages/ # Route-level pages (Login, Dashboard, etc.)

├── services/ # API connectors (Axios logic)

├── redux/ # Store config and slices

├── utils/ # Helpers (e.g. Password Validation, Toast)

└── App.js # Route definitions

##  How to Run Locally
bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Bishes7/Frontend-library-management-system.git

# Install dependencies
cd Frontend-library-management-system
npm install

# Start dev server
npm run dev

